What changed:
- Added missing blank-line paragraph breaks in dense prose blocks so paragraph boundaries are consistently separated by a blank line.
- Improved markdown list flow around the Aristotle quote block (ensured proper spacing before/after the numbered list).
- Added KaTeX-visible equation numbering tags for all in-text referenced equations:
